title: Indiana Historical Society Publications
additional-notes: The first issue renewal shown here is for the 1951 publication of 'A Home in the Woods'.  The renewal record in the registered works database does not specifically mention this serial, but it was originally published as one of its issues that year.

Some issues of this serial have distinctive titles.  Before concluding that such an issue is in the public domain, search for book renewals under its distinctive title. We have not systematically searched individual issue titles past 1951.
acknowledgement: Thanks to Nat Bender for copyright research on this title.
